## Python SDK Example

```python
response = api.get(
    '/api/v1/data/corva/wits/',
    params={
        'query': json.dumps({'asset_id': event.asset_id}),
        'limit': 500,
        'sort': json.dumps({'timestamp': -1}),
        'fields': 'timestamp,data.hole_depth,data.bit_depth,data.weight_on_bit'
    }
)
```

